      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_7QNphG": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What makes Nam Nam different from other candy brands?",
            "icon": "question_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>We don’t make mass-produced candy ,we make <strong>handcrafted joy</strong>. Every Nam Nam product starts from a small idea (and a big craving), made in limited batches with ingredients you can actually pronounce. We call it <strong>“snack magic, made real.”</strong></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_BV4X9a": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Are your chocolates and candies suitable for kids?",
            "icon": "snowflake",
            "row_content": "<p>100%! Kids (and kids-at-heart) love Nam Nam. All our products are made without alcohol or harmful additives or preservatives,so they’re safe and fun for all ages.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_cbK4XH": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Where do you deliver and how long does it take?",
            "icon": "price_tag",
            "row_content": "<p>We deliver Pan-India 🌍!</p><p>Orders usually ship within <strong>24 hours</strong> and reach most metros in <strong>2–5 days</strong>. You’ll receive live tracking updates as soon as your order is on its way.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_XarnmX": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What if my order arrives melted, broken, or damaged?",
            "icon": "truck",
            "row_content": "<p>Don’t worry -we’ve got your back! If anything arrives in less-than-perfect condition, just drop us a WhatsApp or email with a picture within <strong>48 hours</strong>, and we’ll <strong>replace it or refund you instantly</strong>. No questions, no stress.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_nnHKid": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long do Nam Nam products stay fresh?",
            "icon": "lightning_bolt",
            "row_content": "<p>Most Nam Nam goodies (like brittles, popcorn, and candies) stay perfectly fresh for <strong>6–9 months</strong> when stored in a cool, dry place -no refrigeration needed. Each pack has a “Best Before” date mentioned on it for your peace of mind.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_Y4JzEM": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do you use preservatives or artificial colours/flavours?",
            "icon": "leaf",
            "row_content": "<p>Nope! We’re all about <strong>real ingredients and real joy</strong> - no artificial colors, no harmful preservatives. Just honest flavours, premium nuts, real chocolate, and the crunch that comes from careful crafting, not chemicals.</p>",
            "page": ""
